    {
      "id": "t1",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "TikTok has become one of the fastest-growing platforms for creators to build audiences and earn money online. Millions of creators publish videos daily, but many people still wonder how much TikTok actually pays."
    },
    {
      "id": "t2",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "The truth is that TikTok creators earn money through several different sources including the"
    },
