      "id": "t3",
      "tag": "strong",
      "text": "Creator Rewards Program, brand sponsorships, affiliate marketing, and product sales"
    },
    {
      "id": "t4",
      "tag": "p",
      "text": "While TikTok does provide direct payments through its creator program, the majority of earnings for successful creators come from brand partnerships and external monetization."
    },
